<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Gdata throws Zend_Gdata_Exception sometimes, and Zend_Http_Client_Exception (or its subclasses) other times.  This is confusing.  Please make Zend_Gdata throw only Zend_Gdata_Exception or subclasses.</p>

<p>Also there is only one Zend_Gdata_Exception, but the nature of the exceptions take multiple forms.  Please make more exception subclasses to make the distinction more clear.</p>

    </div>
