            <p>Created the following exceptions:</p>

<ul><li>Zend_Gdata_AuthException: the user's credentials were not accepted.</li>
<li>Zend_Gdata_BadMethodCallException: a method was called for a service that does not accept it (e.g. post() for CodeSearch).</li>
<li>Zend_Gdata_HttpException: Http-related issues, or re-thrown Zend_Http_Client_Exception.</li>
<li>Zend_Gdata_InvalidArgumentException: the application tried to set a parameter to an invalid value (e.g. a calendar projection value of "banana").</li>
</ul>
